{"tid":1800819,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【靚過班佳麗】郭可盈撐林文龍做亞視副總裁 明晚任亞姐主席評審","createTime":"2019-12-28T07:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T13:47:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"783deb667c45a987b8be035c747f558055b3fd8b","tid":1800819,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"演戲演足30多年的林文龍，5日前忽然現身亞姐選美宣傳活動，宣佈擔任下月一日正式擔任亞視副總裁，當日並由亞視執行董事兼聯席主席鄧俊杰及亞視非執行董事兼聯席主席賴彩雲向林文龍頒發職員證。雖然亞視屢傳財困，且更不斷裁員，但仍有錢聘請林文龍擔任副總裁，實在令人驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n林文龍當日在記者會上，被問到會否邀請太太郭可盈出山時，林文龍還表示：「應該唔會，因為係要個女批唔批，個女嘅權力比較大。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，郭可盈雖然未有出山演出，但就答應為明晚於亞視大埔總台舉行的《亞洲小姐2019總決賽》擔任大會主席評審，畀足面老公。郭可盈是1993年港姐出身，相信明晚她與林文龍定成焦點，肯定蓋過一班候選亞姐風頭。至於明晚還有任賢齊、鄭欣宜、麥潔文任表演嘉賓，陳啟泰和金剛等司儀，而明晚錄影後，將安排於下月4日在亞視App和香港開電視播出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191228/large/1577517307_0fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191228%2Flarge%2F1577517307_0fef.jpg&h=2d69dd89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191228/60426379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191228%2F60426379&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPMljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=e3b7d3dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191228%2F60426379&h=81a9146c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191228/60426379</a>"},{"pid":"79411c3178bd68d91e8ceb2dd20e1b9f956e0d20","tid":1800819,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:48:26.000Z","msg":"未執咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd756d29144ea41ff3c0c14886d94aad18f342b","tid":1800819,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:49:28.00